    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Toys for babies and toddlers specially made to hang in or above a crib. They usually have a suspension system like a mobile or play arch, or can be attached around the edge like a play spiral.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
